{"tha-ap297:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap297:0.2":"Citakapujakavagga ","tha-ap297:0.3":"Gosisanikkhepakattheraapadana ","tha-ap297:1.1":"“Aramadvara nikkhamma, ","tha-ap297:1.2":"gosisam santhatam maya; ","tha-ap297:1.3":"Anubhomi sakam kammam, ","tha-ap297:1.4":"pubbakammassidam phalam. ","tha-ap297:2.1":"Ajaniya vatajava, ","tha-ap297:2.2":"sindhava sighavahana; ","tha-ap297:2.3":"Anubhomi sabbametam, ","tha-ap297:2.4":"gosisassa idam phalam. ","tha-ap297:3.1":"Aho karam paramakaram, ","tha-ap297:3.2":"sukhette sukatam maya; ","tha-ap297:3.3":"Sanghe katassa karassa, ","tha-ap297:3.4":"na annam kalamagghati. ","tha-ap297:4.1":"Catunnavutito kappe, ","tha-ap297:4.2":"yam sisam santharim aham; ","tha-ap297:4.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap297:4.4":"santharassa idam phalam. ","tha-ap297:5.1":"Pancasattatikappamhi, ","tha-ap297:5.2":"suppatitthitanamako; ","tha-ap297:5.3":"Eko asim mahatejo, ","tha-ap297:5.4":"cakkavatti mahabbalo. ","tha-ap297:6.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap297:6.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap297:6.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap297:7.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma gosisanikkhepako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap297:8.1":"Gosisanikkhepakattherassapadanam pancamam. "}